Title: Patriots And Tyrants
Plot: Jake and Hawkins have one chance to expose the conspiracy behind the Cheyenne government to the independent Texas administration. However, getting there proves to be the most difficult part of their plan.
GuestStars: David Meunier, Timothy Omundson, Daniel Benzali, Chris Kramer, Xander Berkeley, Brian Tee, Geno Monteiro, John M. Jackson, Roxana Brusso, Rick Federman, Dennis Staroselsky, Dominic Hoffman, Laura Leyva, Holt Boggs
